  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/4710f4196aa4b6e115627a5aac59a7ce.poster.avif?t=1767346785\" width=320 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/4710f4196aa4b6e115627a5aac59a7ce.webm?t=1767346785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VZX Player generates awesome audio reactive graphics in real time from any audio source - music player, YouTube, microphone, line-in etc.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>VZX Player has been used by multiple twitch streamers and DJ's and is enjoyed by many home users and tech enthusiasts.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feature Highlights</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple \"visuals\" (a.k.a. \"individual scenes\" or \"graphical effects\") </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Toggling on and off visuals and packs of visuals </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can visualize audio from one audio device at a time - microphone, line-in or what is currently playing </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy tweaking of parameters for many of the visuals - for instance color, saturation and camera rotation speed </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blackout support (F12)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/29d9667e10389924e23b44aae901e78c.poster.avif?t=1767346785\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/29d9667e10389924e23b44aae901e78c.webm?t=1767346785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Input Support</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI is 100% controllable with Game Controller, mouse and keyboard </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key remapping of most input actions  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/c9707106741666ebabe3d92b303d5fee.poster.avif?t=1767346785\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/c9707106741666ebabe3d92b303d5fee.webm?t=1767346785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Display support</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1080p, 4k and high-frequency monitor support (144Hz)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ultra wide monitor support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Display on any secondary monitor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfectly position and scale the window for advanced streaming setups</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Performance</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Low CPU usage for the basic visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >< 500 MB RAM used when all basic visuals loaded</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When program launches, only visuals that are in the current playlist are loaded.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trailer Music \"Gold in you\" by Ashleigh Ball</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/4710f4196aa4b6e115627a5aac59a7ce.poster.avif?t=1767346785\" width=320 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/4710f4196aa4b6e115627a5aac59a7ce.webm?t=1767346785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VZX Player generates awesome audio reactive graphics in real time from any audio source - music player, YouTube, microphone, line-in etc.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>VZX Player has been used by multiple twitch streamers and DJ's and is enjoyed by many home users and tech enthusiasts.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feature Highlights</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple \"visuals\" (a.k.a. \"individual scenes\" or \"graphical effects\") </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Toggling on and off visuals and packs of visuals </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can visualize audio from one audio device at a time - microphone, line-in or what is currently playing </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy tweaking of parameters for many of the visuals - for instance color, saturation and camera rotation speed </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blackout support (F12)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/29d9667e10389924e23b44aae901e78c.poster.avif?t=1767346785\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/29d9667e10389924e23b44aae901e78c.webm?t=1767346785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Input Support</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI is 100% controllable with Game Controller, mouse and keyboard </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key remapping of most input actions  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/c9707106741666ebabe3d92b303d5fee.poster.avif?t=1767346785\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981590/extras/c9707106741666ebabe3d92b303d5fee.webm?t=1767346785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Display support</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1080p, 4k and high-frequency monitor support (144Hz)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ultra wide monitor support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Display on any secondary monitor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfectly position and scale the window for advanced streaming setups</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Performance</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Low CPU usage for the basic visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >< 500 MB RAM used when all basic visuals loaded</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When program launches, only visuals that are in the current playlist are loaded.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trailer Music \"Gold in you\" by Ashleigh Ball</p>",
